textContent:
--- may the 4th be with you---

Okay di naman may ngayon pero baket ba. Kakatapos ko lang star wars and di parin ako maka move on. Anyhoo. Happy 4th monthsary bbycakes!!!! YAYY!!! Goal naten is forever pero ano ba, we need to celebrate every month mwaaaa. 

I'm so happy na later, mabibili ko narin birks mo sa wakas!! I hope you'll be sosososo happy with and that you'll like! You've already given me a lot of gifts that made happy (you included. Pati narin yung star wars na napakaganda huhuhy tysm), and I just want to make you as happy as I am too!! 

Ang dami ko rin adjustments na nangyari this (last) month kase sobrang daming ganap, and I just want to thank you again for always supporting me and caring for me and loving me constantly. I love you so much my forever princess!! My feelings for you will never falter and I always dream of the day na araw araw na tayong magkasama!!! Happy 4th monthsary ulit bbycakes!!!
